&lt;p data-start=&quot;795&quot; data-end=&quot;953&quot;&gt;We see &lt;strong data-start=&quot;802&quot; data-end=&quot;831&quot;&gt;caregivers as our clients&lt;/strong&gt;, too. Our job is to support you, advocate for you, and place you in assignments where you can succeed and stay long-term.&lt;/p&gt;
