&lt;p&gt;Our Continuous Care program is built around consistency—for both clients and caregivers. Instead of scrambling for shifts each week, you&#39;ll be matched with long-term clients and a predictable schedule you can count on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Tandem Care, we believe caregivers deserve the same level of support we provide our clients. Our team works hard to place caregivers in assignments that fit their skills, availability, personality, and preferred service area, creating long-term relationships rather than short-term staffing solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What This Role Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Long-term client assignments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One-on-one care in the client&#39;s home&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ongoing support from a dedicated care team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stable hours with predictable schedules&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opportunities to build meaningful relationships with clients and families&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Role Is a Great Fit If You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Want stable hours and consistent assignments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have experience with dementia care, personal care, mobility assistance, and overnight supervision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy building long-term relationships with clients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Value communication, reliability, and teamwork&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to work for a company that supports and advocates for its caregivers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This Role Is Not a Fit If You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are only looking for occasional or on-call shifts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
