&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are uncomfortable providing hands-on personal care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are uncomfortable assisting with bathing, toileting, incontinence care, transfers, or dementia-related behaviors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
