&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1weojvn&quot; data-start=&quot;776&quot; data-end=&quot;798&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;780&quot; data-end=&quot;798&quot;&gt;Evening Home Care Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;41&quot; data-end=&quot;91&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;41&quot; data-end=&quot;91&quot;&gt;Part-Time | Monday–Saturday | 5:00 PM–10:00 PM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;93&quot; data-end=&quot;186&quot;&gt;Not everyone wants to work mornings—and not every operations job needs to be 40 hours a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;188&quot; data-end=&quot;570&quot;&gt;At Tandem Care, we&#39;re looking for someone who thrives in the evening hours and enjoys being the person who keeps everything running smoothly behind the scenes. While our caregivers are out caring for clients, you&#39;ll be monitoring the schedule, responding to caregiver questions, helping resolve last-minute issues, and making sure every evening shift gets off to a successful start.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;572&quot; data-end=&quot;774&quot;&gt;This isn&#39;t a sales role or a customer service call center. It&#39;s an operations position for someone who enjoys staying organized, thinking on their feet, and making sure nothing falls through the cracks.&lt;/p&gt;
